summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Milwaukee Land Company, an Iowa Corporation, to certain lands in Section Eighteen (18), Township Twenty-two (22) North, Range Eight East W. M., and in Section Six (6) of Township Twenty-two (22) North, Range Nine (9) East, W. M., all in Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating Sixty-six and Ninety-four Hundredths ($66.94) Dollars from Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund for the payment of said lands.
